name: Verify All URLs Respond And Contain Basic Elements
fullName: Test Suites.health check all URLs.Verify All URLs Respond And Contain Basic Elements
description:
Test steps:
1. Extract all URLs from variables_urls.robot
2. For each URL:
   - Open the URL
   - Verify that the URL responds with an HTTP status code of 200 (OK)
   - Verify that the URL contains the basic elements (header, footer and menu)
   - Close the page
